《'''洛城法網'''》（{{lang-en|''L.A.Law''}}）是一部於 1986 年 9 月 15 日至 1994 年 5 月 19 日在美國[[國家廣播公司|國家廣播公司]]電視網首播的法律劇。該劇反映了 20 世紀 80 年代到 90 年代初期美國社會文化和意識形態上的衝撞，劇中將這些衝突，例如：[[墮胎|墮胎]]、[[種族主義|種族主義]]、[[LGBT法律|同性戀權利]]、[[同性戀恐懼症|同性戀恐懼症]]、[[性騷擾|性騷擾]]、[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]和[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]等熱門問題反映到劇中的案件上。<ref>{{cite news|title=L.A. Law Eyes Fear of Police : Television: An upcoming episode on the public's loss of trust includes camouflaged references to the beating of Rodney G. King.|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=1991-03-21|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1991-03-21/entertainment/ca-797_1_police-brutality|accessdate=2010-12-12|first=Steve|last=Weinstein|archive-date=2012-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111133704/http://articles.latimes.com/1991-03-21/entertainment/ca-797_1_police-brutality|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite news|title= Nbc's New 'L.a. Law': The Verdict Is Great|publisher= 洛杉磯時報|date= 1986-09-15|url= http://articles.latimes.com/1986-09-15/entertainment/ca-11948_1_l-a-law|accessdate= 2010-08-24|first= Howard|last= Rosenberg|archive-date= 2012-01-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120111134203/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-09-15/entertainment/ca-11948_1_l-a-law|dead-url= no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite news|title=TV Turns the Other Cheek Again : Television is a victim of the You Can't Win Syndrome. Once, its violence was criticized as unrealistic; now, 'L.A. Law's' Christian character is under fire.|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=1993-10-18|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1993-10-18/entertainment/ca-47167_1_christian-character|accessdate=2010-12-12|first=Howard|last=Rosenberg|archive-date=2012-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111134803/http://articles.latimes.com/1993-10-18/entertainment/ca-47167_1_christian-character|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同時劇中也反映了律師樓裡高薪的資深律師與初級員工在薪酬問題上的對抗。本劇由史蒂芬·布奇柯和特里·路易斯·費舍爾製作，故而帶上了一系列“布奇柯式”的標籤，例如：大量的平行劇情、社交戲碼和“打破[[第四牆|第四牆]]”的幽默。

